File upload successful

File deletion successful

Only warning: "file not public" ‚Üí expected behavior

This is a private storage system, not a public CDN.

Expected Behavior

Cloud icon appears in Media Library grid view
‚Üí This indicates ‚Äústored remotely + private‚Äù
‚Üí This is normal and correct

