## üß† Why It‚Äôs Built This Way
- Public site should stay lightweight and open
- Private life deserves its own controlled space
- Separate systems = cleaner security + less risk
- Cloudflare gives speed + free + control
- WordPress gives private login + emotional space
- Storage can grow gradually

